              </div>
              <div class="card testimonial-card">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.Lm_jc0e50KVZV4tVYKXm6gHaE7?w=262&h=201&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.5&pid=1.7" class="card-img-top rounded-circle mx-auto d-block mt-3" alt="User 2">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">John Smith</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">"Blogging here is easy and fun! I’ve learned so much and made so many connections!"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card testimonial-card">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.57Hz4yPDIPbYnWnKFYtwVgHaL4?w=197&h=316&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.5&pid=1.7" class="card-img-top rounded-circle mx-auto d-block mt-3" alt="User 2">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">John Smith</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">"Blogging here is easy and fun! I’ve learned so much and made so many connections!"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card testimonial-card">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.4v_P5SS6FQgye4Y4kysO4gHaE8?w=202&h=135&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.5&pid=1.7" class="card-img-top rounded-circle mx-auto d-block mt-3" alt="User 2">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">John Smith</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">"Blogging here is easy and fun! I’ve learned so much and made so many connections!"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    <% } %>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Blogger. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
